{"type": "article", "id": 18246, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-30T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004156vGKHaDNF2xkyItXl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是美国的设计事务所 Moniker SF 为一个夫妻组合的巧克力品牌 MITA CHOCOLATE 设计的包装。用不同颜色的背景区分巧克力的口味，但上面的图案和文字只有黑白两色。白色的线条勾画出有几何感的图案，无限复制但跳跃着排列，非常活泼。而品牌的logo“MITA”也设计成了几何线条的感觉，原本的一条笔画变成了三条，简洁而有设计感，与包装相呼应。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004154nAD8UcI93VRWfFu2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004155x3lHnsZuSVzcXokr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004155jtPVxYfZFaQy9HrN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004156Tuox4GHpJFnP7v5z.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}